Doc,<br><br>
You guys caught each other doing the same thing.  Each wanted to prove the other a liar or worse.  We are all guilty to trying to kick each other to death.  It is the normal escalation of war.<br><br>
There is no right and wrong in the heat of battle, just the need to be the last one standing.  I think you both understand that fact and quite frankly so do I.  I don,t know where we can go from here, but I do know I am not going to waste my time confirming anything on anybody.<br><br>
I will decide on what I see on this site.  Two intense guys that do not agree and choose to never agree.  We can continue until we are all victims.  I don't wish that to happen.  It is very hard for me to take this position.  You must know that.  You and I do not agree on a great many things.<br><br>
I am committed to saving this site, but not at the expense of Cook or you.<br><br>
Reaction.  Cook takes some good shots.  You then take some better ones and so on.  The reality is your post on Cook left me cold and sleepless.  I shared that with Cook.<br><br>
I choose to ignore all comments.  I can't deal with it.<br><br>
I don't want to deal with it.  I do not want you guys to make up.  I just want coexistence at best.<br><br>
They are my BOC.
